title: ADD_POP_MULTIPLIER_SPHERE
content:
0x32C7A7E8C43A1F800xCE4A3D20// AddPopMultiplierSphere
int ADD_POP_MULTIPLIER_SPHERE(float x, float y, float z, float radius, float pedMultiplier, float vehicleMultiplier, BOOL p6, BOOL p7);This native is adding a zone, where you can change density settings. For example, you can add a zone on 0.0, 0.0, 0.0 with radius 900.0 and vehicleMultiplier 0.0, and you will not see any new population vehicle spawned in a radius of 900.0 from 0.0, 0.0, 0.0. Returns the id. You can have only 15 zones at the same time. You can remove zone using REMOVE_POP_MULTIPLIER_SPHERE
